---
// THE LAB — the experiments hall. Since the multiverse edition (2026-07-11)
// each experiment was ADOPTED by one universe and wears its full brand — the
// door plates carry the keeper's swatch + number. The doors are tall
// DOORWAYS, each with a living pattern inside (pure CSS transform/opacity
// animation on inline SVG). Clicking one floods the screen with ink
// (curtain) and steps through to the static experiment at /labs/<name>.html.
//
// V3.0 (2026-07-20): the multiverse collapsed to one site, and the lab's
// per-load skin roll went with it — the portal now wears the site's own
// brand (the old skin 02) permanently. The experiments keep their adopted
// universe brands: the lab is where the other universes live on.
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#FAFAF7" />
    <title>LAB — TRES.</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Hanken+Grotesk:wght@400;700;800&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <!-- tracking: one bootstrap for the whole site (Umami + Clarity + visitor id + self-exclusion) - public/ts.js -->
    <script is:inline defer src="/ts.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <a class="back" id="back" href="/">← back</a>

